Pre-Game Insights: India and Australia lock horns in the fifth match in ODI World Cup 2023 on Sunday, October 8.
Australia has often held the upper hand in this historic rivalry, securing victory on 8 occasions.
India enters the ICC World Cup 2023 as one of the frontrunners, bolstered by a talented squad.
As hosts of the tournament, the Men in Blue not only relish home advantage but also field a formidable team.
Australia's performance in ODIs this year has been full of ups and downs.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Chepauk Stadium pitch traditionally favours spin bowlers, creating a heaven for spinners.
Batting first is generally seen as an advantage here, as chasing becomes an arduous task due to the pitch's deteriorating condition.
